{"tid":2188773,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"內蒙搜捕129示威者  官媒員工倒戈反抗","createTime":"2020-09-04T12:29:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-05T13:32:04.000Z","uid":25558,"like":575,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":108,"replies":[{"pid":"7bb074d081d29e5e382a7f99a2b25554361becb9","tid":2188773,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T12:29:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200904/J7HMJJAW2REMXMQU7QAWINM4VQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200904%2FJ7HMJJAW2REMXMQU7QAWINM4VQ%2F&d=HMiOmB7b1AqxO%2BCwCPl1ccRCHeky4xD%2FQbA%2BfbsvJuc%3D&h=e9954779\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200904%2FJ7HMJJAW2REMXMQU7QAWINM4VQ%2F&h=b6e0322f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200904/J7HMJJAW2REMXMQU7QAWINM4VQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n內蒙搜捕129示威者 <br />\n官媒員工倒戈反抗<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/gQMzUWeJ2S2GiXN1tdGmmTt0SKw=/2094x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/WLYZCPXHG5C4XBPLMTCDFWPOFE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FgQMzUWeJ2S2GiXN1tdGmmTt0SKw%3D%2F2094x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FWLYZCPXHG5C4XBPLMTCDFWPOFE.jpg&h=840eac50&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■內蒙近日有多間學校的學生舉行示威。<br />\n<br />\n內蒙人民和平反對中共強行在新學年實施的漢化教學，事件未落幕，警方已急不及待要大抓捕，在網上通緝過百人，並公開他們的「大頭照」，要他們盡早歸案。但是內蒙人民依然堅持抗爭，官方電視台、電台員工聯署，表明寧可失去職業，也不願接受「重漢輕蒙」的雙語教學。<br />\n<br />\n根據南蒙古人權信息中心最新一份通訊，有兩名蒙古族家長據報因為被強迫要送孩子回校，不忿輕生。信息中心又指，縱然面對政府的壓力及警方的恐嚇，內蒙有越來越多人參。。。<br />\n<br />\n通遼市各區的公安局前日開始在網上發「協查通告」，通緝一些被指在學校門外「尋釁滋事」的民眾，當中最誇張的是科爾沁區公安分局。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n逼公職送孩子回校<br />\n<br />\n通遼市其他公安分局也發出協查通告，扎魯特旗、奈曼旗、科左中旗均附上大頭照片和文字形容涉案者的身體特徵，但都只是分別。。。<br />\n<br />\n內蒙古要求小學和初中一年級新學年起部份語文科轉用漢語授課，引來蒙古族人反彈，連。。。。<br />\n<br />\n南蒙古人權信息中心/《蘋果》記者<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/MvD80D-_bqXIUSD-izfRUYwAh5U=/2100x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/AFOFNCEDE5CHHMVD7H7GBKUUCM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FMvD80D-_bqXIUSD-izfRUYwAh5U%3D%2F2100x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FAFOFNCEDE5CHHMVD7H7GBKUUCM.jpg&h=cf77e250&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■內蒙警方發出大頭照通緝示威者。"},{"pid":"49071712ec61bab8ccb6c9513df11b312aa55973","tid":2188773,"uid":54460,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T12:31:14.000Z","msg":"。。。"},{"pid":"1ad3b2563a7f027c75d19960840dea92853f1a80","tid":2188773,"uid":254450,"like":315,"dislike":2,"score":313,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T12:41:10.000Z","msg":"起來！不願做奴隸的人們！<br />\n把我們的血肉，築成我們新的長城！<br />\n（東突/吐蕃/蒙古/滿州/香港）民族到了最危險的時候，<br />\n每個人被迫著發出最後的吼聲。<br />\n起來！起來！起來！<br />\n我們萬眾一心，<br />\n冒著敵人的炮火，前進！<br />\n冒著敵人的炮火，前進！<br />\n前進！前進！進！"},{"pid":"726f3232de1a9d73c7b169b5eb070d145176662f","tid":2188773,"uid":13065,"like":158,"dislike":1,"score":157,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T12:45:52.000Z","msg":"解放軍倒戈先報啦 對住呢個政府冇槍係唔得"},{"pid":"c13c21e93d40183a55a217f3eb350971dfc82b27","tid":2188773,"uid":259901,"like":45,"dislike":1,"score":44,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T12:46:44.000Z","msg":"14億新內蒙古人已經stand by<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bd8dafb7e4d07e53defefe14216dd1f9b5d9f07","tid":2188773,"uid":15815,"like":95,"dislike":1,"score":94,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T12:50:18.000Z","msg":"一味想摧毀本土變大陸化<br />\n香港你都管pat 屎收檔啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n根本一早學足97 前咁管<br />\n做好中港區格唔係求其融合<br />\n咁先玩得耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cc9a5b578894e9941239569e0c25887b0df2e6e","tid":2188773,"uid":60527,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"reply